{"article_id":"BRYvUVEVeDpdRcZn","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Congrats , fellow paranoiacs --","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"you were right .","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"The AP reports :","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"The Internal Revenue Service inappropriately flagged conservative political groups for additional reviews during the 2012 election","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"to see","depth":12},{"id":5,"text":"if they were violating their tax-exempt status ,","depth":12},{"id":6,"text":"a top IRS official said Friday .","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"Organizations were singled out","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"because they included the words `` tea party '' or `` patriot '' in their applications for tax-exempt status ,","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"said Lois Lerner ,","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"who heads the IRS division","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"that oversees tax-exempt groups .","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"In some cases , groups were asked for their list of donors ,","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"which violates IRS policy in most cases ,","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"she said .","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"`` That was wrong .","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"That was absolutely incorrect ,","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"it was insensitive","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"and it was inappropriate .","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"That 's not how we go about selecting cases for further review , ''","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"Lerner said at a conference","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"sponsored by the American Bar Association .","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"`` The IRS would like to apologize for that , ''","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"she added .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Lerner said","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"the practice was initiated by low-level workers in Cincinnati","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"and was not motivated by political bias .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"After her talk , she told The AP","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"that no high level IRS officials knew about the practice .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Agency officials found out about the practice last year","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"and moved to correct it ,","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"the IRS said in a statement .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"The statement did not specify","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"when officials found out .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"Let me see","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"if I 'm understanding this correctly .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"We 're told that","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"( a ) `` low level '' IRS workers in Cincinnati established the practice","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"of deliberately flagging `` tea party '' and `` patriot '' groups for further scrutiny ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"( b ) this was somehow not `` motivated by political bias , ''","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"and ( c ) zero IRS higher-ups were aware","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"that this was going on .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"What a tale .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Did this become a national policy ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"or was it limited to southwest Ohio ?","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"The story","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"linked above","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"says","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"that 75 different conservative groups were affected by this supposedly `` grassroots '' IRS procedure .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"Also , if the IRS brass discovered the malfeasance last year","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"( coincidentally , an election year ) ,","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"why is the public just finding out about it now ?","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"And how can they make the `` no political bias '' claim with a straight face","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"when it appears that only groups on the Right were ensnared by this ?","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"In any case , heads will have to roll over this , right ?","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Wrong :","depth":5},{"id":56,"text":"IRS on conf call","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"no disciplinary action against employees","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"who targeted tea party groups for extra scrutiny .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"- Karen Tumulty","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"( @ ktumulty )","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"May 10 , 2013 -","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"So this actually happened on today 's IRS conference call :","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"The senior IRS official","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"briefing the press","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"just said :","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"`` I 'm not good at math . ''","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"- Zachary A. Goldfarb","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"( @ Goldfarb )","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"May 10 , 2013","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"Today , I call on the White House to conduct a transparent , government-wide review","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"aimed at assuring the American people","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"that these thuggish practices are not underway at the IRS or elsewhere in the administration against anyone ,","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"regardless of their political views .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"Last year , amid reports","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"that the Obama administration was using the levers of executive power","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"to harass conservative political groups in Kentucky and elsewhere ,","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"I issued a \"","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"Today ' s acknowledgement by the Obama administration","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"that the IRS did in fact target conservative groups in the heat of last year ' s national election","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"is not enough ..","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"Last year , amid reports","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"that the Obama administration was using the levers of executive power","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"to harass conservative political groups in Kentucky and elsewhere ,","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"I issued a very public warning to the administration","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"that the targeting of private citizens on the basis of their political views would not be tolerated .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"Today ' s apology by the IRS is proof","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"that those concerns were well founded .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"But make no mistake ,","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"an apology won ' t put this issue to rest .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"Now more than ever we need to send a clear message to the Obama Administration","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"that the First Amendment is non-negotiable ,","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"and that apologies after an election year are not an sufficient response to what we now know","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"took place at the IRS .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"This kind of political thuggery has absolutely no place in our politics .","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"\" I 'll leave you with three flashbacks :","depth":3},{"id":97,"text":"President Obama jokes about auditing political adversaries in 2009 ,","depth":5},{"id":98,"text":"via Glenn Reynolds.","depth":5},{"id":99,"text":"Tea Party groups complain about IRS harassment in 2012.","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"The waves away those concerns as not credible","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"and applauds the IRS","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"for `` doing its job . ''","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"Ahem.","depth":5},{"id":104,"text":"- An IRS spokesperson is now clarifying","depth":5},{"id":105,"text":"that disciplinary action may be taken after all .","depth":5},{"id":106,"text":"Sen. Mitch McConnell is demanding a full , government-wide investigation :","depth":4},{"id":107,"text":"- On May 5 , President Obama urged Ohio State graduates to reject `` cynical '' voices","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"who warn about government abuses and `` tyranny . ''","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"On May 10 , the Internal Revenue Service admitted abusing its power","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"to hurt organizations of a particular political bent during a contested election year .","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"And how 's this for an apology line ?","depth":5},{"id":112,"text":"`` Mistakes were made . ''","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":225,"left":208,"right":224,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":208,"left":114,"right":207,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":114,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":207,"left":182,"right":206,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":182,"left":166,"right":181,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":145,"right":165,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":135,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":126,"right":134,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":118,"right":125,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":2,"right":117,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":117,"left":116,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":3,"right":115,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":125,"left":122,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":119,"right":121,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":9,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":123,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":132,"right":133,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":129,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":15,"right":128,"relation":"restatement","nu